PART 6: THE MONADIC BIND — TRANSITION MATRIX
  M[parent_class, strip_config] = child_class
  This is the CORE of the monadic structure
======================================================================

  n=4: new strip has 2 tiles (arcs from vertex 4)

  Transition table: 2 parent classes x 4 strip configs
   Parent      Strip ->                Child classes (ci: count)
     0(H= 1)     (0, 0) -> 0(H=1): 1, 3(H=3): 1
